In 2018, Guangzhou Xinyi XXX Village.

She was sold to a 40-year-old bachelor in the village as a wife about 25 years ago. They gave birth to a son who is now studying out of town. She is autistic, can't speak, and has no name. She has no hukou and no medical care, so she has never seen a doctor for more than 20 years. Her husband locks her in the kitchen when he goes out to work.